    "Name": "Quark C",
    "Details": "The C configuration emphasizes close-range firepower through a dual SRM 6 arrangement mounted in each arm, fed by two tons of ammunition split between the torsos. Two ER Medium Lasers, one in the right torso and one head-mounted, provide a credible threat at medium range. The combined alpha strike output is disproportionate for a 20-ton frame, though armor protection remains thin.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Communications</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
